{"tid":114833,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"33歲澳洲索模Miranda爆26歲未婚夫好傳統 性行為要等結婚春宵夜","createTime":"2017-02-10T05:57:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T04:31:31.000Z","uid":9573,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"77c09536a017817c07a636253fca08e6222c15a0","tid":114833,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T05:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170210/large/1486703781_0195.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170210%2Flarge%2F1486703781_0195.jpg&h=4bfbc45f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n擁有天使臉孔、魔鬼身材嘅33歲澳洲索模Miranda Kerr，同26歲Snapchat老闆Evan Spiegel訂婚7個月，唔少人都葡萄Evan咁有福氣抱得美人歸。不過Miranda最近喺訪問中唔覺意爆未婚夫係個好傳統嘅人，兩人等待到新婚之夜先上床。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170210/large/1486703783_e98f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170210%2Flarge%2F1486703783_e98f.jpg&h=fd4ba0e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMiranda接受英國《The Times》男記者Richard Godwin訪問，長期擔心對方出軌 祖藍爆同亞男相處之道係&hellip;兩人大談生育問題。Richard表示自己唔打算再生BB，Miranda即刻追問：「咁你用乜嘢避孕方法？你中途掹出嚟？」男記者就俾Miranda咁大膽嘅提問嚇親，回答話用避孕藥。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170210/large/1486704846_2f3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170210%2Flarge%2F1486704846_2f3f.jpg&h=f82f3289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMiranda就爆自己冇食緊避孕藥，同埋未嘗試再造人仔。之後Miranda就爆：「我哋要得結咗婚先，我伴侶係好傳統。」男記者追問Miranda解釋吓伴侶點傳統，Miranda就尷尬咁話:「我哋唔可以.....我意思係我哋....仲等緊。」記者話Miranda講到呢個位睇落有啲失落。記者回應對佢呢個剖白感到驚訝，Miranda就爆笑。"},{"pid":"235f57248d93a534f455910b8e447c16be6c5cf7","tid":114833,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T05:58:52.000Z","msg":"26歲 snatchat 老細 真識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71d275a0e00f962cef942caf788670bb799bbad","tid":114